<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I did not found a hint in the docs that some of the resource plugins are stored in the registry. So I stored them myself in it, e.g. Zend_Translate with key 'translate' - so it available twice in the registry...</p>

<p>This was confusing to me and causes some discussion in the german zfforum.de:
<a href="http://www.zfforum.de/showthread.php?p=46707">http://www.zfforum.de/showthread.php?p=46707</a></p>

<p>Translate, locale and navigation (maybe others) are stored in the registry when using the resource plugins. So a hint in the docs would be great i think..</p>

